To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private EaseOfMovementValue _emv;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_emv = EMV(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_emv.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "easeofmovementvalue", _emv.Current.Value);
}

symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
